Rating: 3
This dish was so easy to make and yet looks so attractive. Perfect for a small dinner party! Can't wait to make it again! (My cornish hens needed 1 hour in the oven)

Rating: 3
I really enjoyed this recipe. It was very tasty and moist! I'd definitely make this again.

Rating: 3
This was really good. I would definitely make the stuffing again and again. But unless you and your "honey" are really big eaters, this can serve up to 4 (unless you happen to have a teenage boy in the house!)